      "Don't be late!",
      "Mark your calendar",
      "You're probably thinking: \"You don't plan anything\"... well I'm a changed person",
      "Can't wait to spend some quality time together ðŸ¥°"
    ].sample %>
    </p>
    <p>Love, <br><%= @user.name %></p>
  </body>
</html>
